were across the street with us,

00:00:14.230 --> 00:00:15.110
I'm Liz Cohen.

00:00:15.110 --> 00:00:16.750
I'm Dean of the
Radcliffe Institute

00:00:16.750 --> 00:00:18.730
for Advanced Study at Harvard.

00:00:18.730 --> 00:00:22.150
