Johnson-Kulukundis Family Art

00:05:16.130 --> 00:05:17.510
Gallery.

00:05:17.510 --> 00:05:20.750
We believe, as an institute
for advanced study,

00:05:20.750 --> 00:05:25.610
that it is our responsibility
to be both timely and timeless

00:05:25.610 --> 00:05:29.030
and that our support
of inquiry is even more

00:05:29.030 --> 00:05:32.920
necessary in tumultuous times.

00:05:32.920 --> 00:05:36.070
You can see this conviction
in Radcliffe's offerings

00:05:36.070 --> 00:05:39.220
this past year, from
our current exhibition

00:05:39.220 --> 00:05:42.490
about the history of
Title IX to our science

00:05:42.490 --> 00:05:46.120
symposium on the impact of
climate change on the world's

00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:51.550
oceans to our conference on
universities and slavery.

